    "blurb": "Four beacon monoliths in four redoubts. Keep one lit to dawn — or light all four at night and call the ship.",
    "newFeatures": [
      "BEACON DEFENSE: four lights, keep one burning",
      "Relight dark beacons by day — 8 shards",
